race.description: Icon Signs (N/P) Tg 5+W Series F Pr2 Division1
race.comment: PRINCESS TO BURN (1) ran fourth in a Other last time, copping a check in the run and finishing 4 lengths from the winner over 305m at this track. Has three wins from Box 1. Can find winning form here. BULSARA (2) goes very well this course and distance starting nine times for three wins and five minors. Placed last time (17.85) at this track in a Other, finishing third and beaten 1.5 lengths. Looks suited here and can measure up. ASTON RAMONA (8) has been without a win for a while, the latest jumping from an outside draw when fourth (17.96) at this track in a Other. Has a good record at this journey. Has the ability to give this a shake. SHE'S FIRED UP (5) cannot be left out after placing here at this trip last start.
